  31 Mar 2010; Justin Lecher <jlec@gentoo.org> clapack-3.2.1.ebuild,
  clapack-3.2.1-r1.ebuild:
  [static] -> [statis-libs], as consequence of #312465

*clapack-3.2.1-r1 (18 Mar 2010)

  18 Mar 2010; Justin Lecher <jlec@gentoo.org>
